docs.lead_paragraph: Four hundred and eighty-one persons were buried in this City last week. The number is one less than the week preceding, and about the expected average for the season. Consumption killed 63 of them. Of course by this word "consumption" is meant almost all sorts of diseases upon which a cough attends, which the physician fails to cure.
